6.

	a)
	
	case 1: i < j		# hops = j-i. Will be clamped between 1 and 6 hops
	
	b)
	
	Add links:
	0 to 2
	1 to 3
	2 to 4
	3 to 5
	4 to 6
	5 to 7
	6 to 0
	7 to 1
	
	c)
	
	2 to 5 takes 2 hops. One from 2 to 4, then 4 to 5.
	6 to 0 takes 3. 6 to 0, 0 to 2, 2 to 3.
	
